re>\r\n                <p class=\"link\"><span class=\"label\">詳細をみる</span></p></a></div>\r\n            <div class=\"item swiper-slide\"><a class=\"box n4\" href=\"https://answers.khi.co.jp/ja/energy-environment/20210731j-01/\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n                <h3 class=\"title-bar\"><span class=\"en\"><span class=\"label\" data-splitting>ANSWERS</span></span><span class=\"ja\"><span class=\"label\" data-splitting>日本がめざすカーボンニュートラルとは？</span></span><span class=\"ja\"><span class=\"label\" data-splitting>脱炭素を成長の原動力へ</span></span></h3>\r\n                <figure class=\"fig\"><img src=\"/assets/images/home/fig_content_a_04.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\r\n                <p class=\"link blank\"><span class=\"label\">詳細をみる</span></p></a></div>\r\n            <div class=\"item swiper-slide\"><a class=\"box n5\" data-aos-delay=\"300\" href=\"https://answers.khi.co.jp/ja/voices/20200731j-02/\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n                <h3 class=\"title-bar\"><span class=\"en\"><span class=\"label\" data-splitting>ANSWERS</span></span><span class=\"ja\"><span class=\"label large\" data-splitting>「つぎの社会へ、信頼のこたえを」</span></span></h3>\r\n                <figure class=\"fig\"><img src=\"/assets/images/home/fig_content_a_05.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\r\n                <p class=\"link blank\"><span class=\"label\">詳細をみる</span></p></a></div>\r\n            <div class=\"item swiper-slide\"><a class=\"box n6\" data-aos-delay=\"600\" href=\"https://answers.khi.co.jp/ja/connected-society/20210131j-01/\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n                <h3 class=\"title-bar\"><span class=\"en\"><span class=\"label\" data-splitting>ANSWERS</span></span><span class=\"ja\"><span class=\"label\" data-splitting>患者と医師を支えるテクノロジー。</span></span><span class=\"ja\"><span class=\"label\" data-splitting>手術支援ロボットが起こす革命</span></span></h3>\r\n                <figure class=\"fig\"><img src=\"/assets/images/home/fig_content_a_06.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\r\n                <p class=\"link blank\"><span class=\"label\">詳細をみる</span></p></a></div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <footer class=\"foot-root\" id=\"js-foot-root\">\r\n      <div class=\"links\"><a class=\"text blank\" href=\"https://www.khi.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\"> 川崎重工業株式会社オフィシャルサイト</a><a class=\"banner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" href=\"https://answers.khi.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/assets/images/common/thm_foot_01.png\" width=\"170\" alt=\"\"></a><a class=\"link\" data-aos=\"fade-down\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzfhPd8i2-rpMSE6Ey0Oeyg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/assets/images/common/thm_foot_02.png\" width=\"96\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\r\n      <div class=\"foot\">\r\n        <address class=\"cr\">Copyright &copy; Kawasaki Heavy Industries, Ltd. All rights reserved.</address>\r\n        <div class=\"misc\"><a class=\"link\" href=\"https://www.khi.co.jp/cookie_policy/\" target=\"_blank\">クッキーポリシー</a><a class=\"link\" href=\"javascript:Bootstrapper.gateway.openModal();\"> クッキー詳細設定</a></div><a class=\"totop js-smooth-scroll\" href=\"#top\"></a>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </footer>\r\n    <script src=\"/assets/js/main.js\"></script>\r\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://api.crm.i-myrefer.jp/track/L2wH15crfNBkkAhVWzd3ie7AYljigUSnS7tWHHDFFXdq310o6X/mt.js\"></script>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.khi-saiyo.jp/recruit/handicapped.html","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T21:04:59.173Z"}